69
00:03:29,627 --> 00:03:30,731
Hard time.

70
00:03:30,816 --> 00:03:34,502
Isn't that great.
They all came back to see me.

71
00:03:34,506 --> 00:03:37,280
That's right.
All except the successful ones.

72
00:03:37,287 --> 00:03:39,160
Now guess what, kids?

73
00:03:39,166 --> 00:03:42,842
