150
00:07:16,087 --> 00:07:19,392
Yeah, well, my mom says
you're a selfish lover.

151
00:07:19,398 --> 00:07:21,331
I know what I want
and I get it.

152
00:07:23,365 --> 00:07:25,612
I'll trash you in my memoirs!

153
00:07:25,625 --> 00:07:27,761
Pay attention you'll be writing
my memoirs.

154
00:07:27,768 --> 00:07:29,592
I'll never last here.

155
00:07:29,596 --> 00:07:31,150
Chin up, little gofer.

156
00:07:31,178 --> 00:07:33,433
You can succeed with Krusty.

157
00:07:33,436 --> 00:07:36,800
A few hints: Always carry a cigar
in case he asks.

158
00:07:36,816 --> 00:07:38,102
Never meet his gaze.

159
00:07:38,106 --> 00:07:41,761
And if he mentions
Mitzi Gaynor, and he will,

160
00:07:41,767 --> 00:07:45,263
